	<div style=3D"width: 80%; float: left">Naked Single, Hidden Single</div>
	<div style=3D"clear: both"></div>
	<div style=3D"width: 20%; float: left">Easy</div>
	<div style=3D"width: 80%; float: left">Naked Pair, Hidden Pair, Pointing
		Pairs</div>
	<div style=3D"clear: both"></div>
	<div style=3D"width: 20%; float: left">Medium</div>
	<div style=3D"width: 80%; float: left">Naked Triple, Naked Quad, Pointing
		Triples, Hidden Triple, Hidden Quad</div>
	<div style=3D"clear: both"></div>
	<div style=3D"width: 20%; float: left">Hard</div>
	<div style=3D"width: 80%; float: left">XWing, Swordfish, Jellyfish,
		XYWing, XYZWing</div>
	<div style=3D"clear: both"></div>
</div>

<p>
	<strong>Button: Hint</strong>=20
	<br>
	Request a hint to find the next cell to
	solve. A hint will either identify a cell which can be solved or a cell
	or cells where candidates can be removed. If candidates are entered on
	the grid, those candidates will be used to help provide a hint,
	otherwise the solver will generate the candidates in the background. <br>
	<span style=3D"color: red"> Please Note: If the candidates entered are
		wrong or incomplete, the solver will not be able to provide a correct
		hint. </span>
</p>
			<p>
	<strong>Button: Generate</strong>
	<br>
	Generate candidate values for all empty cells
	<br>
	<br>

	<strong>Button: Remove</strong>
	<br>
	Removes all candidates from all cells
	<br>
	<br>

	<strong>Checkbox: Edit Candidates</strong>
	<br>
	When checked candidates can be edited using the keyboard
	You can edit candidates using the keyboard or the mouse.
	<br>
	<br>

	<strong>Editing Candidates using the Keyboard</strong>
	<br>
	- Click the Edit Candidates checkbox first.
	<br>
	- Click in the cell you want to edit
	<br>
	- Type the candidate number to add it
	<br>
	- Type the candidate number again to remove it
	<br>
	- Type the DELETE Key to remove all candidates in a cell
	<br>
	<br>

	<strong>Editing Candidates using the Mouse</strong>
	<br>
	- Click in an empty cell
	<br>
	- Click on the position of a candidate to add it
	<br>
	- Click on a candidate to remove it
</p>			<p>
